<seg id="412">Reducing the number of bids was allowed by previous legislation.</seg>
<seg id="413">For the construction of a ring road, the contracting authority did not define, in the notice of initiation of the restricted procedure or in the qualification documents, the values by which it would assess the extent to which the qualification criteria were met or the number of candidates to be invited.</seg>
