<seg id="473">SAO</seg>
<seg id="474">Criteria for the selection of candidates</seg>
<seg id="475">During the construction of the road circuit, the applicants did not have information about what data about their qualifications would be evaluated and how.</seg>
<seg id="476">For the action related to the development and modernisation of waterways and ports, the tender notice for participation in the restricted procedure did not set out criteria for limiting the number of tenderers.</seg>
<seg id="477">All eight candidates fulfilled the qualifications, but this exceeded the number to which the contracting authority restricted participation in the procurement procedure.</seg>
