<seg id="847">23. During the examination of selected intra-community transactions in cooperation with BRH, it was also found that the Czech payer reported intra-community deliveries to the German payer in SH for the 1st to 4th quarter of 2005 with a total value of CZK 240,411,163 (EUR 8,071,823) and another Czech payer reported intra-community deliveries to the German payer in SH for the same period with a total value of CZK 263,470,776 (EUR 8,846,050).</seg>
